tatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371520/extras/2bba207e425d4eb57b41684e885af1a4.poster.avif?t=1752017240\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371520/extras/2bba207e425d4eb57b41684e885af1a4.webm?t=1752017240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371520/extras/2bba207e425d4eb57b41684e885af1a4.mp4?t=1752017240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Market and Online Orders</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can restock supplies by shopping at the market or placing online orders. However, online orders can be a bit pricey. Managing your budget wisely will make your job much easier!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371520/extras/a5e853c0e8cf32c05ea4b2ba75fdc20d.poster.avif?t=1752017240\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371520/extras/a5e853c0e8cf32c05ea4b2ba75fdc20d.webm?t=1752017240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371520/extras/a5e853c0e8cf32c05ea4b2ba75fdc20d.mp4?t=1752017240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>So, What Would You Do If This Tea House Was Yours?</i></h2>",
